quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  23,75,"aur agar hum un par reham karen aur jo takleifein un ko poanch rahi hain, woh daur kar dein to apni sar kashi par uray rahen ( aur ) bhataktay ( phrin )"
  23,76,aur hum ne un ko azaab mein pakra to bhi unhon ne khuda ke agay aajzi nah ki aur woh aajzi karte hi nahi
  23,77,yahan taq ke jab hum ne par azaab shadeed ka darwaaza khol diya to is waqt wahan na umeed hogaye
  23,78,aur wohi to hai jis ne tumahray kaan aur ankhen aur dil banaye. ( lekin ) tum kam shkrgzari karte ho
  23,79,aur wohi to hai jis ne tum ko zameen mein pedakiya aur isi ki taraf tum jama ho kar jao ge
  23,80,"aur wohi hai jo zindagi bakhshta hai aur mout deta hai aur raat aur din ka bdalty rehna isi ka tasarruf hai,kiya tum samajte nahi"
  23,81,baat yeh hai ke jo baat aglay ( kafir ) kehte they isi terhan ki ( baat yeh ) kehte hain
  23,82,kehte hain ke jab hum mar jayen ge aur matti ho jayen ge aur istikhwan ( boseedah ke siwa kuch ) nah rahay ga tokiya hum phir uthaye jayen ge ?
  23,83,yeh wada hum se aur hum se pehlay hamaray baap dada se bhi hota chala aaya hai ( aji ) yeh to sirf aglay logon ki kahaniyan hain
  23,84,kaho ke agar tum jantay ho to batao ke zameen aur jo kuch zameen mein hai sab kis ka maal hai ?
  23,85,jhat bol utheen ge ke khuda ka. kaho ke phir tum sochte kyun nahi ?
  23,86,( un se ) pucho ke saat asmano ka kon maalik hai aur arsh azeem ka ( kon ) maalik ( hai? )
  23,87,"be sakhta keh den ge ke yeh ( cheezein ) khuda hi ki hain, kaho ke phir tum drtay kyun nahi ?"
  23,88,kaho ke agar tum jantay ho to batao ke woh kon hai jis ke haath mein har cheez ki badshahi hai aur woh panah deta hai aur is ke maqabil koi kisi ko panah nahi day sakta
  23,89,"foran keh den ge ke ( aisi badshahi to ) khuda hi ki hai, to kaho phir tum par jaadoo kahan se par jata hai ?"
